snippet.title: CLeM - Wake up [Gameplay trailer]
snippet.description:
Wishlist CLeM now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1861440/CLeM/

A voice wakes you. It gives you a purpose. To achieve it you have a notebook with mysterious entries, and an entire house to explore. The moment has arrived to complete your mission. If you desire. If you are able.

Stay tuned for new updates on the game and all Psychotic Adventures on:
- Discord: https://discord.gg/rRutSzc
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/MangoProtocol
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mango_protocol
- Web: https://www.mangoprotocol.com/
